                            <title xml:lang="en" type="desc"/>
                            <note>The second part of a lexicographical work explaining the difficult
                                passages of the Qurʾān and the Traditions. </note>
                            <note>
                        <locus from="1b" to="1b">Fol. 1v</locus> is filled up with a long
                                extract from the work entitled <title xml:lang="ar-Latn-x-lc">Mabāhij al-fikar wa-manāhij al-ʿabar <foreign xml:lang="ar">مباهج الفكر و مناهج العبر</foreign>
