                                  type="standard"
                                  key="n82216252"
                                  ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/3831923">Waṭwāṭ, Muḥammad ibn Ibrāhīm
                                    ibn Yaḥyá, 1235-1318 <foreign xml:lang="ar">الوطواط، محمد بن
                                        إبراهيم، 632-718 هـ</foreign>
                        </persName> on the peoples who
                                inhabited the earth. Incipit: <foreign xml:lang="ar">في ذكر الامم
                                    الذين سكنوا المعمور فصل واما العرب المستعربة</foreign> Some
                                difficult words are explained on <locus from="180a" to="180a">fol. 180r</locus>.</note>
